Test case #1: login with valid credentials

Steps:
1. Open the site url:https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/
2. Input login into the 'username' field: qaauto
3. Input password in the 'password' field: 123456qwerty
4. Click the 'Sign in' button

Expected result: user is logged in. Sign out button is displayed


Test case #2: sign up a new user

Steps:
1. Open the site url:https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/
2. Enter a username into the 'username' field (for example autouser)
3. Enter an email into the 'email' field (for example test@email.com)
4. Enter a password into the 'password' field (for example 111111222222)
5. Click the 'Sigh up for ourApp' button

Expected result: user is signed up. Sign out button is displayed


Test case #3: sign out

Steps:
1. Open the site url:https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/
2. Input login into the 'username' field: qaauto
3. Input password in the 'password' field: 123456qwerty
4. Click the 'Sign in' button
5. Click the 'Sign out' button

Expected result: user is logged out. Sign in button is displayed


Test case #4: private post creation

Steps:
1. Open the site url:https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/
2. Input login into the 'username' field: qaauto
3. Input password in the 'password' field: 123456qwerty
4. Click the 'Sign in' button
5. Click the 'Create Post' button
6. Enter a title 'post title'
7. Enter a body 'post body'
8. Select 'Приватне повідомлення' in the dropdown
9. Click the 'Save new Post' button

Expected result: the post is created. The message 'New post successfully created.' is displayed.

10. Open the 'My profile' page
11. Verify by the title that the created post is displayed.

Expected result: the created post is shown.

Test case #5: Verify that chat can be opened

Steps:
1. Open the site url:https://qa-complexapp.onrender.com/
2. Input login into the 'username' field: qaauto
3. Input password in the 'password' field: 123456qwerty
4. Click the 'Sign in' button
5. Click the 'Chat' button

Expected result: the chat window is opened. Chat title is displayed


